data.description: Seller is open to offers which include seller paid buyer costs!! This home can be purchased with 0% down. BRAND NEW DRIVEWAY!     Nestled amidst lush greenery, this property offers lake access for all your aquatic adventures. Whether you're a boating enthusiast, a canoeing aficionado, or simply someone who appreciates tranquility, this place is your perfect sanctuary. Boat ramp is just 0.3 miles away! It's a boater's paradise! You can also enjoy easy canoeing opportunities right from your backyard with direct private access to Trout Lake.    This gorgeous 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, one-story pool home is an oasis that will surely captivate you with it's split floor plan and natural light. Step outside and you'll find a covered extended lanai that overlooks the large screened-in pool. Sitting on half an acre, this property offers a detached 2-car garage that includes electricity, internet and a music studio with a mini-split A/C that can be used as an office.   Surrounded by mature trees and well-maintained landscapes, this property offers a peaceful retreat from the hustle and bustle. The verdant surroundings promote a serene and more relaxed lifestyle. It's not just a home, it's a lifestyle! Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a piece of paradise. Contact us today for more information or to schedule a viewing.
